snippet.title: Afterparty | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Afterparty is available now on Steam! Complete your Night School Collection: https://store.steampowered.com/bundle/16322/Night_School_Complete_Bundle/

Escape Hell with your best bud in the latest narrative adventure from the creators of OXENFREE. Get it now for Xbox One, PlayStation 4, and PC and Mac here: http://nightschoolstudio.com/afterparty-game/

Starring:
Janina Gavankar as Lola
Khoi Dao as Milo
Ashly Burch as Sam
Erin Yvette as Wormhorn
Dave Fennoy as Satan

Music by SCNTFC
